<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 02:05:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>快速行动和打破常规正在为 Tokenizer 带来回报</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-21/moving-fast-and-breaking-things-is-paying-off-for-crypto-tokenizers</link><description>市场正在对有利于创新的规则的未来进行定价。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQ6TrkMA9IPU/v8/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-21/moving-fast-and-breaking-things-is-paying-off-for-crypto-tokenizers</guid></item><item><title>当价格开始回升时，比特币投资者抛售最多</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-21/for-bitcoin-etf-holders-a-market-recovery-is-a-reason-to-sell</link><description>比特币 ETF 的糟糕流出暴露了加密货币市场结构中一种令人不安的动态：本应吸引买家回归的价格水平也引发了一些最严重的抛售。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igwvQQkAX9gU/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 15:46:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-21/for-bitcoin-etf-holders-a-market-recovery-is-a-reason-to-sell</guid></item><item><title>Blockchain.com 秘密提交美国公开发行文件</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-21/blockchain-com-files-confidentially-for-initial-public-offering</link><description>Blockchain.com Group Holdings Inc. 是最古老的加密服务公司之一，已向美国证券交易委员会秘密提交首次公开募股申请，加入了在该行业最动荡时期之一寻求上市的大量数字资产公司的行列。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iUGdwd2OqRWo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2026 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-21/blockchain-com-files-confidentially-for-initial-public-offering</guid></item><item><title>比特币越来越依赖塞勒的购买机器</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/bitcoin-grows-more-dependent-on-michael-saylor-s-buying-machine</link><description>在其历史的大部分时间里，比特币的价格都是由众多买家推动的：理想主义者、投机者、早期采用者，以及最近寻求新投资组合对冲的机构投资者。需求分散且难以预测。到了 2026 年，两者都不是。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iA6M34Pte9mQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 15:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/bitcoin-grows-more-dependent-on-michael-saylor-s-buying-machine</guid></item><item><title>Tether 收购软银在比特币财务公司的股份</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/tether-buys-out-softbank-stake-in-bitcoin-treasury-firm</link><description>Tether 收购了软银集团 (SoftBank Group Inc.) 在数字资产财务公司 Twenty One Capital Inc. 中的所有权，在寻求将该公司与另外两家企业合并的同时，增强了其对比特币累加器的控制权。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iz7uK6q5yZnk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 12:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/tether-buys-out-softbank-stake-in-bitcoin-treasury-firm</guid></item><item><title>新加坡因“严重违规”而撤销 Bsquared 加密货币许可证</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/singapore-revokes-bsquared-crypto-permit-over-serious-breaches</link><description>新加坡中央银行吊销了当地一家加密货币流动性提供商的主要支付机构许可证，这对于监管机构来说是罕见的举动，因为这个城市国家寻求减轻该行业的风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3oeJKADLOwU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 10:36:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/singapore-revokes-bsquared-crypto-permit-over-serious-breaches</guid></item></channel></rss>